text: The Pinkprint is the third studio album by Trinidadian-American rapper Nicki Minaj. It was released on December 12, 2014, by Young Money, Cash Money and Republic Records. The album's music returned Minaj to her hip hop roots. ==Track listing== Category:2014 albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:Nicki Minaj albums Category:Cash Money Records albums Category:Young Money Entertainment albums
